title: Be Happy For No Reason
itunes:title: Be Happy For No Reason
description:
Episode 148 - Why do people in society think it is normal to be sad or have a crappy attitude but when we walk around always happy and excited people think we are on drugs? In this episode I talk about this topic and dive into how to control your own happiness and not worry about what other think.
